gulo(ang1,ang2,ang3)\n","\n","  else:\n","\n","    print (\"Valores nao formam um triangulo\")\n","\n","if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n","  main()"],"execution_count":3,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["60\n","60\n","60\n","Triangulo agudo\n"]}]}]}